OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy this morning,
OL,6,Fwith some showers over Dumfries and
OL,7,FGalloway and Southern Borders, edging
OL,8,Fnorth towards Edinburgh by afternoon.
OL,9,FA few bright or sunny intervals later
OL,10,Fbut still the chance of a few heavy
OL,11,Fshowers.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers in Lothian and
OL,14,FBorders largely dying out with some
OL,15,Fclear intervals. A few showers
OL,16,Fcontinuing across Dumfries and
OL,17,FGalloway.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
