OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA mostly cloudy day. Mainly
OL,6,Fdry morning with just a few light
OL,7,Fshowers, then some more persistent
OL,8,Frain followed by heavy showers later.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,11,FRather cloudy with some showers on
OL,12,FThursday and early Friday. Brighter
OL,13,Fthereafter with sunny intervals and
OL,14,Fmore scattered showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
